text: Gnathoenia tropica is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Duvivier in 1891. It is known from Cameroon, Equatorial Guinea, the Democratic Republic of the Congo, and Gabon.BioLib.cz - Gnathoenia tropica. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. It contains the varietas Gnathoenia tropica var. irrorata. ==References== Category:Ceroplesini Category:Beetles described in 1891
